channel.title: Need Help
channel.description:
I really need help. Everytime I run a server it says: You don't have JDK 5.0 or 6.0. But I downloaded the latest Java (JDK 6u6).
Also I don't know if I downloaded it correctly. This is what I did:
Step 1. I went to Java.sun.com and Found The Java and Downloaded.
Step 2. Then, after the download finished I opened it. Then, a box popped of the Java downloaded. Then, I clicked start download.
Step 3. After it finished I closed it out.
Is that all you do if it isn't please tell me how.
